{"tid":2409815,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「日間殺人 晚上偷竊 電視撒謊」 封網開槍 裝甲車鎖街 緬人：軍隊嚇不倒我","createTime":"2021-02-16T06:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T22:42:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7412dc42bae0112ae865dc4cec522b8dc2ca24cb","tid":2409815,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210216/4V3KCBWK6ZCGXN2EMMMLYM6CWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210216%2F4V3KCBWK6ZCGXN2EMMMLYM6CWM%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bris81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=4cfe9246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210216%2F4V3KCBWK6ZCGXN2EMMMLYM6CWM%2F&h=e813d52b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210216/4V3KCBWK6ZCGXN2EMMMLYM6CWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n「日間殺人 晚上偷竊 電視撒謊」<br />\n封網開槍 裝甲車鎖街 緬人：軍隊嚇不倒我<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍事政變發生兩周後，軍方態度更趨強硬，昨日凌晨全面禁網八小時後，日間在各地加強兵力。但民眾未被嚇怕，昨早最大城市仰光、首都內比都和其他城市都繼續有示威反對政變，以及要求釋放被拘押的文人政府國務資政昂山素姬。第二大城市曼德勒昨日傳出槍聲，據指有多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：昂山素姬拘押期延至明日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oqMag7lznA4eWI39CjNekTHOfD8=/2310x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/24CYBX24HZFMDHL3CTRAQGB76I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoqMag7lznA4eWI39CjNekTHOfD8%3D%2F2310x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F24CYBX24HZFMDHL3CTRAQGB76I.jpg&h=61ba5e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■央行總部外，有示威者手持抗爭標語，站在裝甲車前示威。<br />\n<br />\n昨天一早在仰光的中央銀行外，有超過1,000人聚集，不遠處泊有軍方裝甲車與幾輛運兵車。而在集會慣常地點蘇雷塔，更有多達十幾輛裝甲車、水炮車等戒備。另有數百名工程系大學生在仰光北部示威。<br />\n<br />\n在南部城市土瓦（Dawei），亦有幾百人上街遊行，有人高舉標語痛批軍方「日間殺人，晚上偷竊，電視撒謊」。隊伍中更有樂隊同行伴奏。首都內比都和曼德勒也有遊行隊伍。仰光一名中年示威者表明不會被軍方嚇怕：「派裝甲車巡邏是要恫嚇我們。但大家仍然上街，不在乎被捕，亦不怕中槍。我們不會停步。我們心裏的懼意正消散。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-QhcCuRZVK3oDRUAeckettwVh9c=/1127x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DHMLR7C6Y5DZBAVY66B4J54XP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-QhcCuRZVK3oDRUAeckettwVh9c%3D%2F1127x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDHMLR7C6Y5DZBAVY66B4J54XP4.jpg&h=9bcb9518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名孕婦無懼軍方打壓，繼續上街反對政變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示威者減 拘五記者<br />\n<br />\n但軍方亦鐵了心要平息反對聲浪。內比都有大約20名學生被捕，群眾隨後在他們被拘留的警署外聚集，要求放人。到傍晚曼德勒有軍人開槍欲驅散群眾，當地學生組織指多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n儘管各地持續有示威，但早前萬人空巷的情形不再，路透社亦指昨天軍方加強部署後，上街人數減少，只是無法斷言是因應軍方動作、還是出現「抗爭疲勞」。有受訪者坦言「無法天天示威」，惟強調「我們不會屈服，只是小休一下」。<br />\n<br />\n網絡監察組織NetBlocks報告，「官方下令的資訊封鎖」導致緬甸昨日凌晨1時起幾乎全面斷網，到早上9時左右始解封，但就算網絡恢復後，緬甸大部份用戶仍然無法使用社交網站。<br />\n<br />\n前晚緬甸一度風聲鶴唳，軍方除了兩周以來第三次使出禁網手段，更首次在晚間出動裝甲車，北部城市密支那（Myitkyina）其後更有軍人發射催淚氣和開槍對付示威者，惟未知是射實彈還是膠彈。當地傳媒發佈照片顯示有人受傷；有記者則報道指有兩人受傷。據指在場的記者有至少五人被拘，昨天俱已獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G4kDPUZXYFiq41iAKDny5OkqDvU=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IMDGYIZ6IVFIPF53O5NEIMOOSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG4kDPUZXYFiq41iAKDny5OkqDvU%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIMDGYIZ6IVFIPF53O5NEIMOOSY.jpg&h=810550a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國駐緬甸大使館外，有駕車的民眾載着孩子來參加示威。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯國轟向人民宣戰<br />\n<br />\n有見出現不尋常「軍隊活動」，美國駐緬大使館前晚向美國公民發就地避難警報，又與英國及歐盟多國大使發聯合聲明，敦促緬甸軍方勿傷害平民。聯合國緬甸人權問題特別報告員安德魯斯則指軍方加強打壓反映已是狗急跳牆，批軍方向人民宣戰、「須承擔後果」。<br />\n<br />\n本月1日的政變，引爆緬甸十多年未見的大型抗議浪潮和公民抗命運動，抗議軍方破壞民主之苗。不過緬甸軍方未因國內怒潮與國際譴責而動搖，堅稱是因為大選有舞弊、故此依法取得權力，揚言並非政變，更指示緬甸傳媒不得形容軍方政變奪權成立軍政府。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yz3Ow1xdUQ8VJNVbe05dbL7MV6Y=/1681x1253/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MOO5LIXCJBA2VJNYDC34XKQ2SM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyz3Ow1xdUQ8VJNVbe05dbL7MV6Y%3D%2F1681x1253%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMOO5LIXCJBA2VJNYDC34XKQ2SM.png&h=bb30c8d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a30496d01f7b37a0a90e0495d6f833a6ecf62a60","tid":2409815,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"願平安"},{"pid":"fde37066476031a222071878a2a20e665ef96311","tid":2409815,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe8a37161346b078076fe9a4a4d938d682f69e1","tid":2409815,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"關我哋撚事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"ee39d635079feaa917227dd520ddddf45a126496","tid":2409815,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"見到未五毛唔想香港人有盟友架，之前仲話奶茶無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255f580f83e1316b038c5a4beb32c105c6b1e312","tid":2409815,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe8a37161346b078076fe9a4a4d938d682f69e1","tid":2409815,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"關我哋撚事咩屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n我地講好左出軍隊就番屋企訓教呀屌你老